Setup / execution guide (for current state)
Use screen_analyzer_v1/ as the runtime root.

cd /workspace/L.D.B-code-setup/screen_analyzer_v1

Create venv + install:

Linux/macOS:

python -m venv .venv

source .venv/bin/activate

pip install -r requirements.txt

Set key:

export OPENAI_API_KEY=...

(Optional) Edit 002_config/002.002_runtime_settings.yaml

confirm camera.source

confirm capture.interval_seconds: 3

Smoke camera:

python 005_scripts/005.002_smoke_capture.py --source 0 --output-dir 008_outputs/smoke

Single-frame API check:

python 005_scripts/005.001_single_frame_analysis.py --image 008_outputs/smoke/<frame>.jpg

Run full app:

python 001_app/002_app_entrypoint.py

Monitor artifacts:

snapshots: 008_outputs/snapshots/

logs: 010_logs/runtime.jsonl

